<title>Evaluating a Limit Using a Table of Functional Values</title>
 <statement id="fs-id1170572627386">
<p id="fs-id1170572550814">Evaluate <m>\displaystyle{\lim_{x\to4}\frac{\sqrt{x}-2}{x-4}}</m> using a table of functional values.</p>
</statement>
<solution id="fs-id1170572203578">
